{{Quote|B-but... the Emperor ''has'' no enemies...! The daily ''information broadcasts'' assure us of this...!|Metalorn worker|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 30">[[Star Wars (1977) 30|''Star Wars'' (1977) 30]]</ref>}}
'''Daily information broadcasts''' were issued on [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]]-controlled [[Metalorn/Legends|Metalorn]]. In addition to keeping workers updated of their work schedules, they fed them [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] propaganda which stated the Empire had no enemies, keeping the populace ignorant of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]].

